{"tid":1534223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭榮鏗意思係咪即係拒絕攬炒？？","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:38:59.000Z","uid":58335,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"9fdacba6a0d3774a0359e66e89e274e7170bf30c","tid":1534223,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:27.000Z","msg":"戴定頭盔先 <br />\n我唔係分化撚<br />\n啱啱睇now電視見到<br />\n<br />\n佢話支持高官被制裁<br />\n即係支持人權民主法案<br />\n<br />\n但係佢話唔想香港普通市民受制裁牽連<br />\n即係唔支持政策法？？"},{"pid":"4f69394fcdd2e129f5f08b4ec04bfd5f2314f32c","tid":1534223,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=d836d9eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"051478787b42649e3276631562608da5c55cf61b","tid":1534223,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"128fc9bd3f7c53bc06467246f598e5ce61e99142","tid":1534223,"uid":293698,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"160fcc4248688075f16ffbc760309f36341bdb05","tid":1534223,"uid":281401,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:49.000Z","msg":"佢地始終有個考慮，係唔放棄淺藍選民，佢地有種妄想：相對中立會拎到淺藍票。"},{"pid":"5a044ae0c6cc88bb4cae21720ba92184b291d837","tid":1534223,"uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"160fcc4248688075f16ffbc760309f36341bdb05","tid":1534223,"uid":281401,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:49.000Z","msg":"佢地始終有個考慮，係唔放棄淺藍選民，佢地有種妄想：相對中立會拎到淺藍票。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:05.000Z","msg":"淺藍睬佢都傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得烏克蘭最尾都要趕走嗰啲所謂反對派議員"},{"pid":"bee099d003c5902a9bcb718afd6abe7acaf39649","tid":1534223,"uid":50658,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"泛民拒絕攬炒好正常<br />\n佢地都係有商家佬後面幫手嫁嘛<br />\n<br />\n但泛民違背連登仔攬炒理念<br />\n論罪當諸<br />\n泛民應該要100%跟足連登仔先啱數"},{"pid":"79d5bfbeb255055dbffa9e2a1ee14d4f0ba3c35f","tid":1534223,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:34.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"9569b9e9841d26c34020d71c6acc9e112f3c0363","tid":1534223,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e64993903a84a9ef72533657a10a19e0fe5ce54a","tid":1534223,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bee099d003c5902a9bcb718afd6abe7acaf39649","tid":1534223,"uid":50658,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"泛民拒絕攬炒好正常<br />\n佢地都係有商家佬後面幫手嫁嘛<br />\n<br />\n但泛民違背連登仔攬炒理念<br />\n論罪當諸<br />\n泛民應該要100%跟足連登仔先啱數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime"