 />\n次次最後果一下就出賣抗爭者 就睇下今次佢地點"},{"pid":"e92524847770ad97c4476fa121ebd3eb3a6543b9","tid":1534223,"uid":161726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e64993903a84a9ef72533657a10a19e0fe5ce54a","tid":1534223,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bee099d003c5902a9bcb718afd6abe7acaf39649","tid":1534223,"uid":50658,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"泛民拒絕攬炒好正常<br />\n佢地都係有商家佬後面幫手嫁嘛<br />\n<br />\n但泛民違背連登仔攬炒理念<br />\n論罪當諸<br />\n泛民應該要100%跟足連登仔先啱數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"制裁香港官員=香港d官收皮<br />\n制裁香港=全香港收皮<br />\n<br />\n咁你問我，有辦法之下想官收皮定全香港收皮，咁係人都揀淨係官收皮。但如果冇辦法既話全香港收皮我都受"},{"pid":"974581320b40f1bd22ac0e3ffefc4326164fd1bc","tid":1534223,"uid":1251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"其實好多就算黃都唔一定支持攬炒<br />\n敵人同目標一致就得<br />\n唔需要所有野100%認同"},{"pid":"1e705be76e199dde4df283aa5a4e26cdc3457a12","tid":1534223,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e92524847770ad97c4476fa121ebd3eb3a6543b9","tid":1534223,"uid":161726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e64993903a84a9ef72533657a10a19e0fe5ce54a","tid":1534223,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bee099d003c5902a9bcb718afd6abe7acaf39649","tid":1534223,"uid":50658,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"泛民拒絕攬炒好正常<br />\n佢地都係有商家佬後面幫手嫁嘛<br />\n<br />\n但泛民違背連登仔攬炒理念<br />\n論罪當諸<br />\n泛民應該要100%跟足連登仔先啱數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"制裁香港官員=香港d官收皮<br />\n制裁香港=全香港收皮<br />\n<br />\n咁你問我，有辦法之下想官收皮定全香港收皮，咁係人都揀淨係官收皮。但如果冇辦法既話全香港收皮我都受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"ed7815